items.sentence: Have you quarreled with your parents this week?
Have you thought about when you want to arrive?
Have you told Tom why you need to go to Boston?
Tom told Mary why he couldn\'t go to her party.
Tom told me he didn\'t sleep at all last night.
Tom knows you better than he knows anyone else.
Tom leaned toward Mary and whispered something.
Tom is one of the most talkative people I know.
I\'m not sure that I can be all that much help.
I can buy what I need at a store near my house.
